snippet.title: STEAM Trailer | Boardquest: Tales of Liria
snippet.description:
Coming to Steam May 2023! 
Boardquest: Tales of Liria is an upcoming turn-based strategy for casual players. Available for PC & MacOS

[The content presented shows work in progress and is subject to changes]
